item.title: Nepali Homework
item.description: Nepali Homework is an Internet based platform where you can find all home construction and building materials in one click. This is your best solution to find construction workers such as plumbers, electrician etc. You can also buy house building raw materials like quality bricks, cements, hardware, sand, marbles, steel, and cements in best price at Kathmandu. Nepali Homework is all in one home building solution. With this website you can start building home with your available budget and your time limit. Also we provide you a digital contract with the construction group who accept your time and budget limit request. This is the best way to make your new house as well as to renovate to old house by instead of your busy schedule.
